        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-11-20 17:20:18.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2:\n> \n> I believe, we are in process of migration and depreciation of CDS Jython. I think we don't want to spend time in writing Python wrapper, At the same time, I don't the priority of this commit with respect to organizations. So please ignore my vote on this.\n\nHello Brinda,\n\nYou are right. No effort is done now in writing python wrapper.\n\nBut, can we have this in Elalto release and in the current master branch just to keep what was done?",
